      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我好像从小就这样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "如果同学要抄我的作业，直接说要抄，我不会给",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:01",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但是他给出我很可怜的理由，比如被爸妈打了，心情太差了，写不下作业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那我就会毫不犹豫的借给他",
