      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你是大学老师啊，当上教授，位高权重，越老地位越高",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "不是有很多老教授会骗女学生吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "谁也说不准以后，所以我在努力让自己不要变成那种人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "这你怎么努力？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我看的书，我接触的朋友都在让我保持一些道德",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "想到成为那样的人，我就觉得很恶心，很可怕",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "所以，绝对不会的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "真的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "真的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，我等会要去忙了，晚点聊吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "写教案改试卷吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "当老师的除了上课还在忙什么？我真想不到了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉你一天天的好忙啊。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "今年是我工作第一年",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "新老师，第一年有很多事情要干，准备评级，副教授要出相应的论文和研究目标",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我等会要去找编辑对出版书的事情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "哇，你还出书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我居然也认识文化人啊。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "不是你想的当作家的出书，我出书是为了评职称",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我现在新人老师都要出书好评职称，这有点像是发论文",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "过核心期刊发论文太难了，出书反而会简单一些",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "原来这样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "教文学的也这么世俗吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "教文学的也要生活，也要吃饭啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我有朋友在五台山当道士，为了考道士证他们要读很多道士的专业书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "方外之人尚且如此，何况于老师呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "读文学，教文学其实没有什么特别的特别的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "就算是特别人，也是在自己的内心世界，但生活秩序中其实都差不多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "等等道士也要考证吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，我刚知道的时候也很震惊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "有证的道士才是正经道士，是官方承认的道士",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "他们一大般看一些老子穷宝通鉴什么的，这就是他们的专业书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "学习到了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "Yeah完全没用的知识又多了一点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "真去忙啦，我跟编辑约好时间了，不能迟到",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "16:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
